OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1777874650
OL,3,CPolice make 10 arrests for alleged
OL,4,Cviolent disorder following football
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FKris Jepson joined Cleveland Police as
OL,8,Fthey arrested ten men who are
OL,9,Fsuspected of being involved in
OL,10,Fviolence after Millwall's win over
OL,11,FMiddlesbrough in April.
OL,13,FPolice have arrested ten men for
OL,14,Fallegedly being involved in violent
OL,15,Fdisorder following a football match.
OL,17,FIt came after Millwall's 2-1 win over
OL,18,FMiddlesbrough at the Riverside Stadium
OL,19,Fon 3 April 2026 with fans reportedly
OL,20,Fclashing outside Middlesbrough railway
OL,21,Fstation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1777874650
OL,3,CPolice make 10 arrests for alleged
OL,4,Cviolent disorder following football
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FThe men were arrested in raids carried
OL,8,Fout over two days as part of Operation
OL,9,FMars.
OL,11,FCleveland Police say the raids were
OL,12,Fintelligence-led and came after CCTV
OL,13,Fand police cameras caught the disorder
OL,14,Fon film. It brings the total number of
OL,15,Farrests to 12 after two people were
OL,16,Farrested on the day of the match.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1777874650
OL,3,CPolice make 10 arrests for alleged
OL,4,Cviolent disorder following football
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FChief Superintendent Martin Hopps told
OL,8,FITV News Tyne Tees that he wanted the
OL,9,Fpolice action to act as a "deterrent"
OL,10,Fahead of the Championship play-offs in
OL,11,Fthe coming weeks.
OL,13,FMiddlesbrough and Millwall could meet
OL,14,Fagain in the semi-finals if both teams
OL,15,Ffail to secure automatic promotion on
OL,16,Fthe final day of the season on
OL,17,FSaturday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1777874650
OL,3,CPolice make 10 arrests for alleged
OL,4,Cviolent disorder following football
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,F"We need to be mindful that they may
OL,8,Fplay Millwall in those play-offs or
OL,9,Fanybody else, so for us it's very much
OL,10,Fabout the deterrent as well," he said.
OL,11,F"If you're going to commit serious
OL,12,Fdisorder or any disorder of any kind,
OL,13,Fthen expect some sort of consequence
OL,14,Fto that disorder."
OL,16,FThe violence occurred after the rival
OL,17,Ffans clashed on Bridge Street West and
OL,18,Fcarried on the disorder into the
OL,19,Frailway station car park.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1777874650
OL,3,CPolice make 10 arrests for alleged
OL,4,Cviolent disorder following football
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FCh Supt Hopps added that he did not
OL,8,Fthink the incident was a return of the
OL,9,Fheight of football hooliganism in the
OL,10,F1980s.
OL,12,F"It's very rarely seen, which is
OL,13,Fgood," he said. "Unfortunately, when
OL,14,Fit is seen, that's when we get back to
OL,15,Fthe message we're going to be strong
OL,16,Fon it because we've had so many
OL,17,Fincidents where we haven't had any
OL,18,Fdisorder and that's what we'd like to
OL,19,Fkeep.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1777874650
OL,3,CPolice make 10 arrests for alleged
OL,4,Cviolent disorder following football
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,F"I don't believe it was organised and
OL,8,Fthe reason for that is just the way it
OL,9,Funfolded on the day. They took the
OL,10,Fopportunity, despite a large policing
OL,11,Fpresence, to air their frustrations
OL,12,Fwith one another.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1777874650
OL,3,CPolice make 10 arrests for alleged
OL,4,Cviolent disorder following football
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,F"As part of our operation, we deploy
OL,8,Fevidence gatherers, equipped with
OL,9,Fcameras, and they track the movement
OL,10,Fof offenders and that leads us to
OL,11,Freally good footage, corroborated by
OL,12,Fthe CCTV, and it lends itself to the
OL,13,Finvestigation and now we're in that
OL,14,Fposition where we understand who is
OL,15,Finvolved, we've taken that firm action
OL,16,Fagainst those individuals over the
OL,17,Flast couple of days."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
